snippet.title: Alice In Stardom - Visual Novel Trailer
snippet.description:
Alice in Stardom is a free GxG visual novel coming to Steam and Itch.Io this April.

You play as Alice, a frustrated intern who stumbles her way into the world's most popular idol reality show. Will you be able to overcome your fellow contestants,and find fame? Or even....love?

Alice In Stardom was created by Crystal Game Works: 

Steam: https://bit.ly/2CMMEkP
Itch.Io: https://itch.io/profile/crystalgameworks
Twitter: https://twitter.com/CrystalGameWork 

Opening Video by Kidd "The Maniac" Bowyer.
Music  Provided by RFM https://youtu.be/svp-9rAs1yo
